fields.name: Frost Ray
fields.description: Attacks the enemy target to Freeze the target for 1 turn with a 15% chance

fields.name: Frost Ray - Purify
fields.description: Attacks the enemy to remove 1 beneficial effect granted on the target and freezez the target for 1 turn with a 15% chance each

fields.name: Frost Ray - Fluctuate
fields.description: Attacks all enemies to Freeze them for 1 turn with a 15% chance

fields.name: Pulverizing Magic Bullet
fields.description: Attacks the enemy target to weaken the target's Defense for 2 turns and decreases the target's attack speed for 2 turns with a 50% chance

fields.name: Pulverizing Magic Bullet - Fluctuate
fields.description: Attacks all enemies to weaken the Defense for 2 turns and decreases their Attack Speed for 2 turns with a 50% chance

fields.name: Pulverizing Magic Bullet - Amplify
fields.description: Attacks the enemy target to inflict damage proportionate to the target's MAX HP, weakens the Defense for 2 turns and decreases the target's Attack Speed for 2 turns with a 50% chance

fields.name: Icy Magic Bullet
fields.description: Attacks all enemies to decrease their Attack Bar by 30% each with a 60% chance

fields.name: Icy Magic Bullet - Absorb
fields.description: Attacks all enemies to absorb their Attack Bar by 30% each with a 60% chance

fields.name: Icy Magic Bullet - Chain
fields.description: Attacks all enemies 3 times to decrease thir Attack Bar by 30% each with a 60% chance

fields.name: Ice Explosion
fields.description: Attacks all enemies and the cooldown of the [Ice Explosion] will be decreased by 1 turn each according to the number of enemies defeated.

fields.name: Freeze Mind
fields.description: Attacks the enemy target to inflict damage proportionate to the target's MAX HP and reduces the target's Attack Bar to 0

fields.name: Frost Wind
fields.description: Attacks all enemies to infict damage and Freezes them for 1 turn

fields.name: Ice Mist
fields.description: Attacks all enemies to inflict 2 Continuous Damage effects for 2 turns. 1 Continuous Damage effect is inflicted additionally for each harmful effect on the enemies with a 50% chance

fields.name: Flame Ray
fields.description: Attacks the enemy target to inflict Continuous Damage for 1 turn with a 50% chance

fields.name: Flame Ray - Flood
fields.description: Attacks the enemy target to inflict Continuous Damage for 1 turn with a 50% chance. The damage increases according to the Attack Speed

fields.name: Flame Ray - Chain
fields.description: Attacks the enemy target 4 times to inflict Continuous Damage for 1 turn with a 50% chance each

fields.name: Flaming Magic Bullet
fields.description: Attacks the enemy target to weaken the Defense for 2 turns

fields.name: Flaming Magic Bullet - Fluctuate
fields.description: Attacks all enemies to weaken the Defense for 2 turns and inflicts Continuous Damage for 2 turns

fields.name: Flaming Magic Bullet - Accelerate
fields.description: Attacks the enemy target to weaken the Defense for 2 turns and increases your Attack Bar by 100%

fields.name: Igniting Magic Bullet
fields.description: Attacks the enemy target to decrease the Attack Speed for 2 turns and disturbs the target's HP recovery for 2 turns with a 50% chance

fields.name: Igniting Magic Bullet - Brand
fields.description: Attacks the enemy target to decrease the Attack Speed for 2 turns and leaves a Branding Effect for 2 turns. In addition, disturbs the target's HP recovery for 2 turns with a 50% chance

fields.name: Igniting Magic Bullet - Chain
fields.description: Attacks the enemy target 3 times to decrease the Attack Speed for 2 turns and disturbs the target's HP recovery for 2 turns with a 50% chance

fields.name: Burn Soul
fields.description: Attacks the enemy target to inflict damage. The damage increases according to the Attack Speed of both you and the target

fields.name: Flaming Thunder
fields.description: Attacks all enemies to inflict damage. The damage increases according to the Attack Speed

fields.name: Eruption
fields.description: Attacks the enemy target to inflict damage. The damage increases by 30% for each harmful effect on the enemy

fields.name: Flame Explosion
fields.description: Attacks the enemy target 4 times to inflict Continuous Damage with each attack for 1 turn. The inflicted damage increases by 20% for each Continuous Damage granted on the target

fields.name: Shock Ray
fields.description: Attacks the enemy target to disturb the HP recovery for 2 turns with a 50% chance

fields.name: Shock Ray - Chain
fields.description: Attacks the enemy target 3 times to disturb the HP recovery for 2 turns with a 50% chance each

fields.name: Shock Ray - Destroy
fields.description: Attacks the enemy target to disturb the HP recovery for 2 turns with a 50% chance and destroys the enemy's MAX HP by 30% of the damage dealt

fields.name: Air Magic Bullet
fields.description: Attacks the enemy target to remove 1 beneficial effect with a 50% chance and decreases the Attack Speed for 2 turns with a 100% chance

fields.name: Air Magic Bullet - Brand
fields.description: Attacks the enemy target to remove 1 beneficial effect with a 50% chance. Decreases the Attack Speed and leaves the Branding Effect for 2 turns with a 100% chance each

fields.name: Air Magic Bullet - Chain
fields.description: Attacks the enemy target 3 times, each attack having a 50% chance to remove 1 beneficial effect of the enemy and 100% chance to decrease the Attack Speed for 2 turns

fields.name: Lightning Magic Bullet
fields.description: Attacks the enemy target to Stun the target for 1 turn

fields.name: Lightning Magic Bullet - Destory
fields.description: Attacks the enemy target to Stun the target for 1 turn and destroys the enemy's MAX HP by 50% of the damage dealt

fields.name: Lightning Magic Bullet - Suppress
fields.description: Attacks the enemy target to Stun the target for 1 turn and increases the skill cooldown time by 2 turns

fields.name: Whirling Wind
fields.description: Attacks the enemy target 3 times to weaken the Defense and leaves a Branding Effect for 2 turns. A huge damage will be inflicted in the end

fields.name: Magic Bullet Madness
fields.description: Randomly attacks the enemies 5 times to decrease the Attack Power for 2 turns. The inflicted damage increases if the same target gets hit again

fields.name: Sharp Wind
fields.description: Attacks the enemy target to destroy the enemy's MAX HP by the damage dealt

fields.name: Soul Shot
fields.description: Attacks the enemy target to increase the target's skill cooldown time by 2 turns. The enemy can't be revived if the enemy is defeated with this skill

fields.name: Light Shock
fields.description: Attacks the enemy to decrease the target's Attack Bar by 15% with a 25% chance

fields.name: Light Shock - Purification
fields.description: Attacks the enemy to remove 1 beneficial effect granted the target and decreases the target's Attack Bar by 15% with a 25% chance each

fields.name: Light Shock - Chain
fields.description: Attacks the enemy 3 times to decrease the target's Attack Bar by 15% with a 25% chance each

fields.name: Operation Alpha
fields.description: Recovers the ally target's HP by 35% and extends the time of beneficial effect granted on the target

fields.name: Operation Alpha - Power-up
fields.description: Recovers the ally target's HP by 35% and extends the time of beneficial effects granted on the target. In addition, increases the Attack Power of all allies for 2 turns

fields.name: Operation Alpha - Accelerate
fields.description: Recovers the ally target's HP by 35% and extends the time of beneficial effect granted on the target. In addition, fills up the ally target's Attack Bar.

fields.name: Operation Beta
fields.description: Recovers the HP of all allies by 20% each and grants immunity for 1 turn

fields.name: Operation Beta - Protect
fields.description: Recovers the HP of all allies by 20% each and grants immunity for 1 turn. Creates a shield equal to 20% of the ally's HP on allies with full HP for 2 turns

fields.name: Operation Beta - Protect
fields.description: Recovers the HP and Attack Bar of all allies by 20% each and grants immunity for 1 turn

fields.name: Fast Pace
fields.description: Makes the Attack Bar of the ally and the enemy to 100%. In addition, increases the Attack Speed of the ally target for 2 turns

fields.name: Counter Phase
fields.description: Increases the Defense of all allies and counterattacks for 2 turns whenever attacked

fields.name: Rock On
fields.description: Increases the Attack Power of all allies for 2 turns. After that, up to 3 allies will attack the enemy target

fields.name: Turning Point
fields.description: Evenly matches the percentage of the HP of all allies and removes all harmful effects. After that, increases the Defense of all allies for 3 turns

fields.name: Dark Shock
fields.description: Attacks the enemy to absorb 10% of the target's Attack Bar with a 25% chance

fields.name: Dark Shock - Purification
fields.description: Attacks the enemy to remove 1 beneficial effect granted on the target and absorbs 10% of the target's Attack Bar with a 25% chance

fields.name: Dark Shock - Chain
fields.description: Attacks the enemy 3 times to absorb 10% of the target's Attack Bar with a 25% chance each

fields.name: Operation Gamma
fields.description: Attacks the enemy to remove all beneficial effects granted on the target with a 75% chance

fields.name: Operation Gamma - Weaken
fields.description: Attacks the enemy to remove all beneficial effect granted on the target with a 75% chance and weaken the Defense for 2 turns with a 50% chance

fields.name: Operation Gamma - Weaken
fields.description: Attacks the enemy to remove all beneficial effects granted on the target with a 75% chance and stuns the target for 1 turn if you successfully remove the beneficial effects

fields.name: Operation Delta
fields.description: Attacks the enemy to elongate the harmful effect granted on teh enemy by 1 turn with a 25% chance

fields.name: Operation Delta - Chain
fields.description: Attacks the enemy 3 times to elongate the harmful effect granted on the enemy by 1 turn with a 25% chance each

fields.name: Operation Delta - Ruin
fields.description: Attacks the enemy to elongate the harmful effect granted on the enemy by 1 turn with a 25% chance. After that, the enemy's HP will be decreased proportionate to the total no. of turns of the harmful effect granted on the target

fields.name: Unbalanced Field
fields.description: Increases the skill cooldown time of all enemies by 2 turns each and decreases the Attack Speed for 2 turns. After that, the skill cooldown time of all allies will be decreased by 2 turns each and the Attack Speed will be increased for 2 turns

fields.name: Lockdown
fields.description: Puts the enemy target to sleep for 3 turns and decreases the Attack Speed of all other enemies for 2 turns. The sleep effect can't be resisted

fields.name: Shock Wave
fields.description: Removes all beneficial effect on all enemies, decreases their Attack Speed for 2 turns with a 30% chance and Stuns them for 1 turn with a 30% chance

fields.name: Analyze Weakpoint
fields.description: Attacks the enemy 4 times to grant a harmful effect that isn't granted on the enemy for 2 turns each amon Decrease ATK SPD/Increased chances of landing a Glancing Hit/Decrease DEF/Decrease ATK/Branding/Unrecoverable Effects
